    <item>
      <title>罗格夫称拜登和特朗普赞成“炸毁”美国债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rogoff-says-biden-trump-favor-blowing-up-debt-low-rates-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学经济学教授肯尼思·罗格夫表示，总统乔·拜登及其前任和挑战者唐纳德·特朗普都有可能将美国债务水平推向危险的境地，因为华盛顿未能认识到超低利率时代不会回来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rogoff-says-biden-trump-favor-blowing-up-debt-low-rates-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登权衡对交易的担忧声明，美国钢铁下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/us-steel-falls-on-report-biden-will-voice-concern-on-nippon-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，总统乔·拜登预计很快将发布一份声明，对新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的提议表示担忧。这家总部位于匹兹堡的公司的股价创下近四年来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/us-steel-falls-on-report-biden-will-voice-concern-on-nippon-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
